query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS economic_indicators (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  indicator_type ENUM('gdp_growth', 'unemployment_rate', 'inflation_rate', 'exchange_rate', 'interest_rate', 'money_supply', 'oil_price', 'stock_index', 'labor_force_participation', 'wage_growth', 'foreign_investment', 'government_spending', 'private_sector_growth', 'youth_unemployment', 'female_participation') NOT NULL,
  indicator_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  value INT NOT NULL,
  unit VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  period VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  period_type ENUM('daily', 'weekly', 'monthly', 'quarterly', 'yearly') NOT NULL,
  data_source VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  source_url VARCHAR(500),
  previous_value INT,
  change_percent INT,
  metadata JSON,
  is_latest BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  fetched_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
